profile_positions.description:
Joined on February 2012 as a Lecturer in the Department of Electrical and Electronic Engineering; 
Took Study Leave from August 2013 to July 2014;
Continued from July 2014 and promoted to Senior Lecturer at the same time;

During my service at the University, I was assigned to accomplish the following duties and responsibilities:
•	Taught Theory and Laboratory sessions for 3 undergraduate courses
•	Supervised final year projects of 3  student-groups
•	Prepared syllabus and routine of the classes
•	Performed duties as the Founder & Adviser of the Leading University Photographic Society (LUPS)
•	Performed duties as the Academic Adviser at the Department
•	Organized first ever Higher Study Seminar in the Sylhet city (2015); Delivered pitch, presented slides to motivate students for pursuing higher study abroad; Also arranged another webinar from Netherlands for prospective Bangladeshi students (2016)
